{
  "stem": "22836.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was building up himself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything the partisans.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave me a gun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was fighting with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We was putting in under trains, was ripping up the trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the most, they put me in-- I was a [NON-ENGLISH], doing-- doing skin, like sheeps sometime I'm making-- I'm making from that to wear, from sheep, the skin.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They call [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But its in Yiddish, called-- they call [NON-ENGLISH] in Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And  they mostly put me in for [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My wife was working there too, help in the kitchen what we need.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we was happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We was happy there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Soon-- soon they come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And even that time, I got a baby, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "All of the sudden, I got a baby, six months old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The name was Szise, after my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a nice little boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Even the [NON-ENGLISH] used to come play with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they give me even a cow with milk for the baby.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "For the-- they was calling him the boss from the Otriad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What happened the end, when when the German, when they start running the German back, and they was coming in our neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they coming in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Let's say like [NON-ENGLISH] was free already from the German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], it was very hard to go straight.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then we have to go all around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In-- in that time, my wife was sick on typhus, on typhus.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Typhus, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't have how to feed the baby.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we couldn't get milk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the baby pass away that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we come without the baby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Pass away the baby.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think everything happen strange, strange happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we come back to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
